
# Overview of the application

This program is really an experiment the goal of which will be to: 

- Import a list of books 
- Import book data
- Store the information in a graph 
- Provide an interface to query the data

In addition, an LLM will be used to support understanding the queries made to the application.

The program will be structured approximately as follows:

- Interface
- LLM
- GraphQL
- Python 
  - neomodel
    - Interacts with neo4j
  - strawberry
    - interacts with GraphQL
- Neo4J